items.description:
AVAILABILITY
This service is available to all residential
consumers within the corporate limits of the City
of St. Martinville. Service(s) will be extended to
all consumers in a separately metered, singlefamily
dwelling for domestic use(s). Such uses
will include lighting, heating, cooking and
refrigeration.
TYPE OF SERVICE
Residential service(s) will be available at singlephase
sixty hertz standard available voltage(s).
Three-phase service is available upon approval
of the City of St. Martinville. Adequate over
current and surge protections shall be the
responsibility of the consumer.
